215270260.text: "TGFbeta modulates cell proliferation by controlling the expression of cell cycle regulating factors, including Cyclin Dependent Kinases (CDKs) like p15, p21, and p27 and cell cycle promoters like cMYC, cyclin D2, CDK2, and cyclin E. TGFbeta also promotes T naive cell differentiation into Treg cells by inducing FOXP3 expression, or into Th17 cells in the presence of IL-6 (XREF_FIG)."
